window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Nightsveil has fallen. Humankind is reeling. It is the start of a war between planes.</b></p> <p>The Primeval Demon, Belzu, continues to wreak havoc throughout the Human Lands. Saffron Merryster shall try to gather the Greater Vampire Families against this threat, Edithe Dawnrise will work to unite her broken company after the company war, and Daniel Song will finally brave his way into Elutra. All of them working separately to tackle Belzu.</p> <p>But Salvos only has one goal: grow stronger.</p>"; 
